Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:46.93,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}向这丑陋的世界轻声说「再见」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.03,0:00:54.63,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}用这对朱色翅膀掩去一切丑陋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.23,0:01:06.73,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,000)}思念如附着的污渍般挥之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:11.23,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在这地球上生存着的人儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:19.13,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}令人窒息般地紧紧相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:25.33,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}凝视着镜中的另一个自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:31.23,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为了隐藏自己的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.03,0:01:38.43,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}去刺伤那些温柔善良的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:44.93,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}向这丑陋的世界轻声说「再见」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.03,0:01:50.83,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}朱色的翅膀轻盈地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:57.23,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}烈火般的热吻一次次重复着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.24,0:02:09.33,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就用这最后一吻收敛起热情奔放的心
Dialogue: 2,0:22:24.84,0:22:31.33,C2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}太阳把热情的目光投向这边
Dialogue: 2,0:22:31.54,0:22:36.73,C2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}真想好好享受这夏天 这阳光
Dialogue: 2,0:22:36.74,0:22:44.13,C2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今天会发生什么令人激情澎湃的事吗
Dialogue: 2,0:22:44.44,0:22:48.83,C2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}小小的不安点缀着这美妙的期盼
Dialogue: 2,0:22:50.44,0:22:56.23,C2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,200)}夏天的回忆涌现在我脑际
Dialogue: 2,0:22:56.34,0:23:02.13,C2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}晶亮的碎片注入天空大海充满世界
Dialogue: 2,0:23:02.24,0:23:06.93,C2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,100)}低声私语请求你的拥抱
Dialogue: 2,0:23:06.94,0:23:09.93,C2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}顽皮地挑逗
Dialogue: 2,0:23:09.94,0:23:14.93,C2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}不需要你做出暧昧的温柔
Dialogue: 2,0:23:16.44,0:23:22.83,C2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,000)}那一瞬 我已经预感到一切
Dialogue: 2,0:23:22.84,0:23:26.73,C2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(000,300)}在这热情洋溢的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.93,0:00:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望就保持现在的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像现在这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要相信健的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像现在这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.03,0:00:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来都这样祈求了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和本人的意识没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.43,0:00:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做就要从周围开始做起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是 事已如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只能改变了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行有疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来马上就要倒不了茶了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,800)}第十话  虚伪的心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  詹妮夫还是不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是正在洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  已经2个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话  脑海里图就会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真像詹妮夫的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑海里图是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  只不过是没睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛  因为每晚都很热吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累的话就不要勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在房间里休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  麻里  你要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和浴香她们出去买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5点爸爸要出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:03:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之前回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  好  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,cheeze
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个到底什么时候能修好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次做  以前也没有做过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样慢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易有的夏天就要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真啰嗦  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要踩那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,困扰了  困扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这边也有心理准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...  要花多长时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实应该问我为什么要在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会太晚的  哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:04:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不会对这点小事计较吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃便当吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作都做完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  上午的都完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纪美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去千佳家了  说是要做暑假作业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上夏天就要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要结束了吗  夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后  秋天会来  冬天会来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春天会来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能同时过着夏天和冬天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有结束  也就不会有开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前也想着这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请给我这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,礼物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不要紧了吗  光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要站在那个地方  坐在那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直沉默的我  平静的我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经决定了  因为我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是今天才决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界是这么的虚幻和美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却...把这个世界给破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几次  几次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光  是不是有什么烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客气  什么都可以跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说这种话  不太像我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,健
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要说对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么样竹本都会被光强走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像他这样的男人 这个世界到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是  就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦  这算是鼓励吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不能再让她哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知什么时候能修好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个摩托修好后一起去兜风吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,0:08:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兜风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和光一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能跑的话  想到任何地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:09:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光有地方想去的话  都能去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  但...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该怎么做才能让她不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人的心情和化掉的冰一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是会变的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然光说了喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光
