Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻里  你为什么生气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢健
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我也喜欢麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.68,0:10:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以...对了  麻里也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本就不想要同情
