Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个卑鄙的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我伤害了麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对麻里做了很过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光  不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是光的错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种时候...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是家里那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快闪开  光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱纽·有司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈 这才是光大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么光会把怪物...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没有变身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说多余的东西搀混过多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某个特定时期繁衍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集合生物的特长可以攻击的特种生物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的生物首先是以化石的形式被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把那个生物称为ET觉醒体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Extinct Definition
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扩张领域也许就是指它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被生物隐藏的第二的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个地球会发生生物的大毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那种程度下  古老的种族被毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生存下来持有力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,则产生充满活力而崭新的飞跃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但新生的不久又衰老
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话又会重复一样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ET觉醒体是周期性的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于灭亡  而实行的防卫本能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是我的结论
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有着作用的答案是改变外表
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有攻击力变线化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事对我和光有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  ET觉醒体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是以她为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是凭本能知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光会给地球带来毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大毁灭会怎么进行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.08,0:15:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,众说纷纭 还没有确定真正的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定马上就能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说谎  说谎  说谎...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西全是你特意编出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是给世界带来灾难的死神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个设想并没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也把光...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所知道的光大人是和你接触而出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是拜求
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.68,0:16:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了  真正的光大人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么了
