Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.98,0:17:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我身体里有两个光的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和黑暗的我战斗  我是这样的想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我和把世界毁灭的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是同一体的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我世界的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咽下这所有的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有底的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个世界完结
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是健所说的死神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  你不是黑暗和死神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温柔又温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我所爱的光
