Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,责任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有痛苦  全部都...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  健
