Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让我想起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于从谁那里得到被爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认真去爱一个人是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要进入我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样真的会害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁  你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我是光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能被别人爱的说谎的光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴  闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是什么
